{
  "stem": "18932.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But she wouldn't give anybody just to, you know, to make us miserable.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, she was a Jewish-- from, I think, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a few Czechs and a few Hungarian kapos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some Jewish-- Polish Jews, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then they got us together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said we have to-- after the bath, when we have already stuff-- and we were going to the next town, which was Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we walked over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I heard somebody say to us, oh, you are lucky you are not going there where the dust is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said, see, Ma, we're not going to work in the streets when it's all the dust.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're going to probably work in a factory where it's going to be clean.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know what they meant-- where it's-- where it's the dust.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they meant we are going to get burned and turned into dust.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we walked to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed there overnight, slept maybe 500 women in one little cubbyhole.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the next morning, they told us to stay in line.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stood in line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were train coming on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was next to my mom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they cut through the lines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One went to one train, and one to the other train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- immediately, I stood behind my mother, so I should be with her together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went on a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we started our journey to a working camp, which happened to be in-- near Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The name of it was Poppenbuttel-Sasel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went to this camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they gave us barracks, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Like, we were, I think, 16 women in one barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was like bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
